<a href="http://mattn.kaoriya.net/software/lang/ruby/20111017205717.htm">http://mattn.kaoriya.net/software/lang/ruby/20111017205717.htm</a>
<a href="http://www.sankitch.me/blog/2012/05/05/build-octopress-on-github-dropbox/">http://www.sankitch.me/blog/2012/05/05/build-octopress-on-github-dropbox/</a>
<a href="http://sesame.github.com/blog/2012/12/09/how-to-use-octopress/">http://sesame.github.com/blog/2012/12/09/how-to-use-octopress/</a></p>
]]></content>
